The hawk flew over the coast of Brazil. He noticed a strange looking 
ship and he descended. 

Jetstorm:
I am Jetstorm and I represent the Tripredacus. I wish to meet those 
responsible of this meeting.

Gogolan:
We are they. I am Gogolan Redfeather. My friend is named Ramiel 
Luminous. We conveined this meeting to discuss about the events on 
this planet.

Ramiel:
As a security precaution, we kindly ask you to leave all sorts of 
armament or weaponry back in the forest. We shall then wait for any 
other Transformer wishing to join the conference.

Jetstorm:
I have just been reformatted and have no way to use weaponry.

Gogolan:Agreed. Please proceed near the table.
